Lynsey Bartilson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lynsey_Bartilson 0 Lynsey Marie Bartilson (born July 1, 1983) is an American actress, dancer, and singer. She is best known for playing Lily Finnerty on the Fox/WB sitcom Grounded for Life. Lynsey_Marie_Bartilson ( born July_1_,_1983 ) is an_American_actress , dancer , and singer .
